- `brca2_loss`
- `msi_high`
- `wnt_activity_score`
- `emt_score`
- `stemness_score`
- `ifn_gamma_signature`
- `hypoxia_score`
- `copy_number_8q24`
- `copy_number_9p21`
- `rnaseq_MYC_log2_tpm`
- `rnaseq_AXL_log2_tpm`
- `rnaseq_SLFN11_log2_tpm`
- `rnaseq_ASCL2_log2_tpm`

### Dependency outcomes
- `dependency_BRAF`
- `dependency_EGFR`
- `dependency_ERBB2`
- `dependency_KRAS`
- `dependency_RIT1`
- `dependency_KIF18A`
- `dependency_TMED10`
