codex
The strongest interaction I found is not one of the receptor oncogenes; it is KIF18A. In colorectal lines, the APC/WNT signal becomes very strong only when `smad4_loss` is absent, while `smad4_loss=1` almost abolishes the KIF18A dependency even in APC-mutant colorectal cells.
